content: Hello! Thanks for contacting XYZ Home Services. Can I get your name, please?
Um, hi, it's Emily. I need some help with my sink.
Thank you, Emily! I can assist you with your sink issue. Could you please share the address where you'd like us to come?
Oh, the address? Umm, let me think... it's on Maple. Or wait, maybe my old apartment? Sorry, what do you need again?
No worries! Just the complete street address where you need the plumber to come, including apartment or unit number if you have one.
It's, um... 18 Maple, I think? Or 18B? Is that what you need? Not sure, I'm at work now.
Thank you! Just to confirm, is it 18 Maple Street, apartment B? May I please have the city and zip code as well, so we make sure we come to the right place?
Uh honestly I can't remember the zip code at all. It's in, um, you know, just by the park? Sorry, I donâ€™t have all that stuff on me now.

No problem, Emily! When you have a chance, could you please send the full address (street, apartment/unit if any, city, and zip)? We need that to book your plumbing appointment and make sure our technician gets to you.
I'll have to check when I get home. Sorry, can I text back later?
